              communities of viewers allow for targeted campaigns for
              subscription wellness programs, supplements and functional food
              and beverage products, fitness apps, and wearables. Key targets
              are the younger Gen Z and Millennial generations who are both
              prioritizing wellness and spending disproportionately more on
