            </p>
            <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
              Marketers and brands have noticed the overall interest in health
              and wellness expanding beyond traditional wellness products to
              other areas including food, beauty, workplace benefits, even
              financial products. Fancy a shot of functional nutrition with
              turmeric, ginger, or extra protein on your next visit to
              Starbucks? The coffee king added these to the menu in 2025.
            </p>
            <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
